      Correspondence
    </span>
  <h1 class="gem-c-title__text gem-c-title__text--long">
    Open letters between HM Treasury and Bank of England, September 2020
  </h1>
</div>
  </div>
  

  <div class="govuk-grid-column-two-thirds">
    
  <p class="gem-c-lead-paragraph">CPI inflation was 0.2% in August 2020, prompting an open letter from the Governor of the Bank of England to the Chancellor on 17 September 2020. The Chancellor replied to the Governor on 17 September 2020.</p>

  </div>
</div>

